<task id = "id137JH300DXW"
    xmlns:ditaarch = "http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/">
<title>Task 4: Conversion Processing</title>
<prolog><author>Scott Prentice</author>
<critdates><created date = "2013-07-19"/>
<revised modified = "2013-07-20"/></critdates></prolog>
<taskbody><context><note><p>Between each step or as needed, remember
to save all files.</p><ul><li conref = "#id131MHH0F0Y4/saveall"></li></ul></note></context>
<steps><step><cmd>Verify <filepath>fm2dita.ini</filepath> file is
set up properly.</cmd>
<info><ul><li>Refer to the FM2DITA documentation for details.</li></ul></info></step>
<step><cmd>Open book created in step 3, open all files.</cmd></step>
<step><cmd>Run the following FM2DITA commands on the book (be sure
to re-select the book with each command, and watch for console errors)</cmd>
<info><ul><li><uicontrol>Assign IDs to Topics in Book</uicontrol></li>
<li><uicontrol>Fix Images in Book</uicontrol></li>
<li><uicontrol>Fix Tables in Book</uicontrol></li>
<li><uicontrol>Fix/Flatten Cross-refs in Book</uicontrol></li>
<li><uicontrol>Merge Code Lines in Book</uicontrol> (use “screen”
default”)</li>
<li><uicontrol>Delete Invalid Attributes in Book</uicontrol> (use
“Id Idref” default)</li>
<li><uicontrol>Delete Unstructured Markers in Book</uicontrol> (use
“Cross-Ref Index” default)</li>
<li><uicontrol>Delete Empty Elements</uicontrol> (run for each empty
element to delete, typically “p” at least)</li></ul></info></step>
<step><cmd>Save all files in book.</cmd></step></steps></taskbody></task>
